{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbd4687d8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s5316"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5316"},"text":"§ 5316.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Transition provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbd4687d9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s5316/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Prohibition on new grants or loans after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1975","children":[],"tail":"; exceptions"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Except with respect to projects and programs for which funds have been previously committed, no new grants or loans shall be made after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1975","children":[],"tail":", under (1) title I of the Demonstration Cities and Metropolitan Development Act of 1966 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3301"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 3301","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], (2) title I of the Housing Act of 1949 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1450"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 1450","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] (3) section 702 or section 703 of the Housing and Urban Development Act of 1965 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3102"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 3102","children":[],"tail":" or 3103], (4) title II of the Housing Amendments of 1955 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1491"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 1491","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], or (5) title VII of the Housing Act of 1961 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1500"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 1500","children":[],"tail":" et seq.]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbd4687da-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s5316/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Final date in fiscal year for submission of application for grant; establishment by Secretary","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of funds available for any fiscal year, the Secretary shall not consider any statement under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s5304/a"},"text":"section 5304(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":", unless such statement is submitted on or prior to such date as the Secretary shall establish as the final date for submission of statements for that year."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbd4687db-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/383/tI/s116"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–383, title I, § 116","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-08-22"},"text":"Aug. 22, 1974","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/652"},"text":"88 Stat. 652","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/375/s15/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–375, § 15(d)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-08-03"},"text":"Aug. 3, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/1076"},"text":"90 Stat. 1076","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/399/tI/s111/h"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–399, title I, § 111(h)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-08"},"text":"Oct. 8, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/1622"},"text":"94 Stat. 1622","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/35/tIII/s309/m"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–35, title III, § 309(m)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/397"},"text":"95 Stat. 397","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/181/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–181, title I","children":[],"tail":" [title I, § 110(a)], "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-11-30"},"text":"Nov. 30, 1983","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/97/1168"},"text":"97 Stat. 1168","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbd4687dc-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbd4687dd-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbd4687de-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Demonstration Cities and Metropolitan Development Act of 1966, referred to in subsec. (a), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/754"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–754","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1966-11-03"},"text":"Nov. 3, 1966","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/80/1255"},"text":"80 Stat. 1255","children":[],"tail":". Title I of the Act was classified principally to subchapter I (§ 3301 et seq.) of chapter 41 of this title, and was omitted from the Code pursuant to this section which terminated authority to make grants or loans under such title I after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 1975","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3331"},"text":"section 3331 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Housing Act of 1949, referred to in subsec. (a), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1949-07-15/ch338"},"text":"act July 15, 1949, ch. 338","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/63/413"},"text":"63 Stat. 413","children":[],"tail":". Title I of the Housing Act of 1949 was classified generally to subchapter II (§ 1450 et seq.) of chapter 8A of this title, and was omitted from the Code pursuant to this section which terminated authority to make grants or loans under such title I after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 1975","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1441"},"text":"section 1441 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Sections 702 and 703 of the Housing and Urban Development Act of 1965 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3102"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 3102","children":[],"tail":", 3103], referred to in subsec. (a), were omitted from the Code pursuant to this section which terminated the authority to make grants or loans under those sections after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 1975","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Housing Amendments of 1955, referred to in subsec. (a), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1955-08-11/ch783"},"text":"act Aug. 11, 1955, ch. 783","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/69/645"},"text":"69 Stat. 645","children":[],"tail":". Title II of the Housing Amendments of 1955 was classified generally to chapter 8B (§ 1491 et seq.) of this title, and was omitted from the Code pursuant to this section which terminated authority to make grants or loans under such title II after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 1975","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1701"},"text":"section 1701 of Title 12","children":[],"tail":", Banks and Banking, and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Housing Act of 1961, referred to in subsec. (a), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/70"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–70","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1961-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1961","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/87/149"},"text":"87 Stat. 149","children":[],"tail":". Title VII of the Housing Act of 1961 was classified generally to chapter 8C (§ 1500 et seq.) of this title, and was omitted from the Code pursuant to this section which terminated authority to make grants or loans under such title VII after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 1975","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1701"},"text":"section 1701 of Title 12","children":[],"tail":", Banks and Banking, and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idbd4687df-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsecs. (c), (d), and (e) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/383/s116"},"text":"section 116 of Pub. L. 93–383","children":[],"tail":" were omitted from this section. Subsec. (c) amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1453/b"},"text":"section 1453(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":", subsec. (d) amended section 3311(b) and (c) of this title, and subsec. (e) amended section 1452b(a) and (h) of this title."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idbd4687e0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1983—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/181"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–181","children":[],"tail":" substituted “prior to such date” for “prior to such date (in that fiscal year)”, and “for that year” for “in that year”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1981—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/35"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–35","children":[],"tail":" substituted provisions relating to submission of required statement for provisions relating to submission of required application."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1980—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/399/s111/h"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–399, § 111(h)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated subsec. (g) as (b) and struck out “or from a unit of general local government for a grant pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s5306/h"},"text":"section 5306(h) of this title","children":[],"tail":"” after “"},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s5306/a"},"text":"section 5306(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":"”. Former subsec. (b), relating to deductions from grants for fiscal year 1975, was struck out."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (f). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/399/s111/h/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–399, § 111(h)(1)","children":[],"tail":", struck out subsec. (f) relating to advances for program period beginning "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 1975","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (g). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/399/s111/h/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–399, § 111(h)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated subsec. (g) as (b)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (h). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/399/s111/h/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–399, § 111(h)(1)","children":[],"tail":", struck out subsec. (h) relating to sources of funds to meet deficiency in fiscal year 1977."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1976—Subsec. (h). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/375"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–375","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (h)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idbd4687e1-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idbd4687e2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1983 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/181/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–181, title I","children":[],"tail":" [title I, § 110(b)], "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-11-30"},"text":"Nov. 30, 1983","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/97/1168"},"text":"97 Stat. 1168","children":[],"tail":", as amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/479/tI/s101/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–479, title I, § 101(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1984","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/98/2220"},"text":"98 Stat. 2220","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/98/479/tI/s101/b/1"},"text":"“The amendments made by this part [part A (§§ 101–110) of title I of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/181/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–181, title I","children":[],"tail":", amending this section, sections 5301 to 5308 and 5312 of this title, and provisions set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s5305"},"text":"section 5305 of this title","children":[],"tail":"] shall apply only to funds available for fiscal year 1984 and thereafter.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idbd4687e3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1981 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/35"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–35","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 1981","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/35/s371"},"text":"section 371 of Pub. L. 97–35","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s3701"},"text":"section 3701 of Title 12","children":[],"tail":", Banks and Banking."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
